{"type":"text","timestamp":1773436297162,"sessionID":"ses_316fcb79fffeLVMPL0QpkiSz53","part":{"id":"prt_ce90a3826001YRTV1d0N6URqg7","sessionID":"ses_316fcb79fffeLVMPL0QpkiSz53","messageID":"msg_ce90a31f1001mncbubqPlUmr0d","type":"text","text":"All done. Here's a summary of what was accomplished in this session:\n\n## Completed Work\n\nThe TDD verification step feature is now fully implemented across 3 commits on `feature/tdd-verification-step`:\n\n### Commit 1 (`e7ae4c8`): Core modules\n- **`src/lib/test-runner.ts`** — Runs test commands (`bun test`), captures exit code/stdout/stderr, parses test counts from bun/jest output formats, extracts error summaries\n- **`src/lib/tdd-verifier.ts`** — Orchestrates test running + test detection, produces `TddVerificationResult` with strict/warn modes, includes text rendering and error summary extraction\n\n### Commit 2 (`fe9d811`): Pipeline integration\n- **`src/lib/verifier.ts`** — Added `TddVerificationResult` to `FullVerificationResult`, added `FullVerificationOptions` type (`skipTests`, `strictTdd`), integrated TDD as step 3 in `runFullVerification`\n\n### Commit 3 (`43b9d3d`): CLI integration (this session)\n- **`src/config.ts`** — Added `strictTdd: false` and `testTimeout: 120_000` defaults to `DEFAULT_CONFIG.tdd`\n- **`src/lib/schema.ts`** — Added `--skip-tests` and `--strict-tdd` flag definitions to both verify and launch command schemas\n- **`src/commands/verify.ts`** — Added `skipTests`/`strictTdd` options, passes them through to `handleBuildVerification`\n- **`src/commands/launch.ts`** — Extended `handleBuildVerification` to accept `FullVerificationOptions`, reports TDD results (pass/fail/warnings/skip) alongside browser results\n- **`src/index.ts`** — Added `skipTests`/`strictTdd` to `CLIArgs`, parses `--skip-tests`/`--strict-tdd` flags, wires them to the verify command, updated help text\n\nBoth `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` pass cleanly.","time":{"start":1773436297161,"end":1773436297161}}}
